# WanHammer
First Game with XCODE Swift - Project 3 - OpenClassRoom's

Welcome to the WanHammer Game :


WanHammer is a Terminal Battle between 2 teaMs
Each Team have 3 Fighters
LifePoint, Strength, Weapon, and Special Attack depend of the fighter's category and a fetich number ! :)


Warrior 	: 
LifePoint 	: 100
Strenght  	: 10
Spécial Attack	: Double Attack


Dwarf	 	: 
LifePoint 	: 80
Strenght  	: 20
Spécial Attack	: Double Damage


Colossus 	: 
LifePoint 	: 200
Strenght  	: 5
Spécial Attack	: Fear (opponent lost his round)


Wizard	 	: 
LifePoint 	: 150
Strenght (care) : 10
Spécial Attack	: FireBall ! (Damage 10 on each opponent)



Also : In WanHammer, there is a random BONUS ZONE : 
If you're fighter is lucky : He can made a lot of damage in the same round
If not....He can made a lot of damage on his team !! 
 

ENJOY IT ! 


Games Rules : 


First step : 
Choose Your :
- User Name
- Team Name
- 3 Fighters (Human || dwarf || magician || Colossus)
- Favorite Number beetween 1 and 5


Second Step : 
The Battle !
- Have a look on the LifePoint of each teams and Fighters.
- Have a look on the last action
- You have to choose which fighter do an action

CHEST ZONE : 
- Sometimes, you have to change your weapon/care at the beginning of the round

DAMAGE : 
- You have to choose on which opponent the action will be done

FETICH ZONE : 
Maybe your fetich number is active ? So The special attack will be executed.

BONUS ZONE : 
If you're fighter is lucky : He can made a lot of damage in the same round
If not....He can made a lot of damage on his team !! 


END OF THE GAME : 
If your fighter's life point fall to 0 : he's dead 
When 3 fighter's of one team are dead, the WanHammer is done !




SORRY FOR MY ENGLISH ;). I'm begginer 

